  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no-- there were no-- no Jewish students in-- in the late '30s included or accepted in the officers school in Poland because it was-- Hitler was well on the way.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Poland used to take one leaf after another from Hitler's book by then.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, sure, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is rather a-- a-- a-- a particular thing worth-- worth mentioning, worth describing because as I said in the beginning of the interview that it was a city of 100,000 people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was economically self-- self-supportive in the sense that it had a core-- core industries that gave the-- the population a economic base and a tempo of life and a rhythm of life and a-- that-- that-- that was not available to many or most of-- of Jewish hamlets and townships.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We talked about the shtetl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The shtetl is [INAUDIBLE] of-- of something otherworldly almost in Jewish-- Yiddish literature and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But all that-- all that description, all that beauty that is attached with it-- and I made slight reference to it when I mentioned my mother's birthplace of [POLISH]-- which was-- that precisely because there was not much material basis, then-- then you had to fill the life with other venues.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had to fill with other-- with other aims, with other ambitions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the man-- the leader-- the creator of the Habima in Israel, the-- the national theater, was born in Horodok.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a friend of my-- of my mother's because that was-- they-- they concentrated on things other-- otherworldly because the worldly offerings were limited or almost non-existent.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
